name: Random Numbers - Red, White and Blue 001
description:
Using Excel to create random number art. This piece cycles through 10 completely unique and impossible to repeat screens, with the colours assigned to numbers generated randomly according to a set distribution: 

dark blue shades: ~10%, 
light blue shades: ~30%,
white: ~15%, 
pink: ~25%, 
red: ~20%

This is the first in a series; Random Number Generated Art. I hope you enjoy it.
